{
  "texts": [
    "We constrain g i [m] to increase and then decrease monotonically so that G i (f) is unimodal and has a single peak value of 1.",
    "Given g i [m], m = 1, …, M, we can determine the peak frequency f proto i and the half-power bandwidth b proto i of G i (f).",
    "The prototype parameters g i [m], m = 1, …, M of each formant filter are time-invariant and are determined during the auto-encoder training.",
    "Compared with ref.",
    "29, we increase M from 20 to 80 to enable more expressive formant filters, essential for synthesizing male speakers' voices."
  ]
}